== 软件系统中的应用 ==
时区信息数据库用来处理时区和进行时区转换，已经应用于很多的计算机系统中，包括：

* [[BSD|BSD]]衍生操作系统，包括[[FreeBSD|FreeBSD]]、[[NetBSD|NetBSD]]、[[OpenBSD|OpenBSD]]、[[DragonFly_BSD|DragonFly BSD]]和[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]；
* [[GNU_C_函式库|GNU C 库]]以及使用它的系统，包括[[GNU|GNU]]、大多数的[[Linux发行版|Linux发行版]]、[[BeOS|BeOS]]、[[Haiku|Haiku]]、[[Nexenta_OS|Nexenta OS]]以及[[Cygwin|Cygwin]]；
* [[System_V|System V Release 4]]衍生系统，例如[[Solaris_(操作系统)|Solaris]]和[[UnixWare|UnixWare]]；
* [[AIX|AIX]] 6.1及更高版本<ref name="Olsontzsetup">{{cite web|title=Olson time zone support and setup|work=AIX 7.1 information|url=http://publib.boulder.ibm.com/infocenter/aix/v7r1/index.jsp?topic=/com.ibm.aix.baseadmn/doc/baseadmndita/olson_time_zone.htm|publisher=IBM|accessdate=2011-03-12|archive-date=2012-08-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69bLPYIMh?url=http://pic.dhe.ibm.com/infocenter/aix/v7r1/index.jsp?topic=%2Fcom.ibm.aix.baseadmn%2Fdoc%2Fbaseadmndita%2Folson_time_zone.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AIXTZ">{{cite web|title=Managing the Time Zone Variable|url=https://www-304.ibm.com/support/docview.wss?q1=tz&dc=DB520&rs=111&uid=isg3T1000252&context=SWG10|publisher=IBM|date=2007-02-02|accessdate=2011-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713001112/https://www-304.ibm.com/support/docview.wss?q1=tz&dc=DB520&rs=111&uid=isg3T1000252&context=SWG10|archive-date=2011-07-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>（自AIX 5.2开始的较早版本，仅为支持[[MySQL|MySQL]]<ref>{{cite web |title=2007 daylight savings time changes for Unix |url=http://www.uic.edu/depts/accc/systems/daylight/unix.html |date=2007-02-25 |accessdate=2008-03-18 |publisher=Academic Computing and Communications Center, University of Illinois at Chicago |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69bLQic74?url=http://www.uic.edu/depts/accc/systems/daylight/unix.html |archivedate=2012-08-01 }})</ref>之类的[[第三方软件|第三方软件]]而加入时区信息<ref name="AIXLinuxinfo">{{cite web|title=AIX O/S updated to support 2007 Daylight Saving Time change|url=http://www14.software.ibm.com/webapp/set2/sas/f/enews/2006/10/DSTupdate.html|date=2007-10-18|publisher=IBM|accessdate=2011-03-12|archive-date=2012-08-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69bLQCWws?url=http://www14.software.ibm.com/webapp/set2/sas/f/enews/2006/10/DSTupdate.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但其并未将时区信息应用到操作系统中<ref name="AIXLinuxinfo"/><ref name="AIXwiki">{{cite web |author= Wickremasinghe, Christopher |title= Introduction of daylight saving time in Western Australia 2006 |ur